data.eml:eml: Two new species of Paraneseuthia Franz (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae) from West Malaysia

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Jałoszyński, Paweł (2014): Two new species of Paraneseuthia Franz (Coleoptera, Staphylinidae, Scydmaeninae) from West Malaysia. Zootaxa 3895 (4): 590-594, DOI: http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3895.4.8
